{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/GIF_V1.gif?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Draw, renovate, decorate, follow the story and note: Gallery is the first coloring book game where you can paint by number and enjoy home design and decorating at the same time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/b.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/Ga_cap_1_en.png?t=1737043394\" />Join our heroes, Mia and Leo, in an amazing adventure: color hundreds of pictures, renovate an old house and fill it with life and fancy decorations, restore an abandoned Art Gallery and dive into a lively story of this adorable couple!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/s.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/GIF_V4.gif?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/b.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/Ga_cap_2_en.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hundreds of unique, high quality paintings</strong> created  exclusively for Gallery.\u00a0Original gameplay: combination of coloring book and home design! Color pictures, get stars and spend them on decorating the house and exploring the story. That\u2019s a creative game for real designers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/s.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/GIF_V5_New2.gif?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/b.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/Ga_cap_3_en.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A variety of locations to explore and to renovate.</strong>\u00a0We have a cozy corner for every taste here!\u00a0Rich and variable decor: there is always more than one option to pick for each and every corner of the house and other locations as well!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/s.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/GIF_V2.gif?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/b.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/Ga_cap_4_en.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wide range of outfits for the main heroes</strong>, Mia and Leo. Want to see Mia as an ancient princess, a movie-star or a race track mechanic? Sure thing! Want Leo to be a giant turkey, a dancer or a fireman? We\u2019ve got it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/s.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/GIF_V3.gif?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/b.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/Ga_cap_5_en.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You can't lose here!</strong> No 'Game over' signs! All you have to do here is color pictures, relax and enjoy the story. We have numerous in-game events waiting for our players where you can get new exclusive paintings to color, decor elements to instal and pets to\u2026 well, to pet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In short - grab a brush, get comfy and let\u2019s paint that world bright!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/b.png?t=1737043394\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/extras/Ga_cap_6_en.png?t=1737043394\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737043394","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/page.bg.jpg?t=1737043394","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/6d154ea8be8be1e9b5f277e2a2057a2b927c600a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737043394","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253860/6d154ea8be8be1e9b5f277e2a2057a2b927c600a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737043394","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"cont